data.description: REDUCED  $75,000. This charming property offers comfort and practicality, featuring granite counters, oversize dark maple cabinets, 20' tile flooring, upgraded carpet, and stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen, overlooking the family room, creates a warm atmosphere for gatherings. A separate dining area and a generous living room provide ample space for everyday living.  The master bedroom, complete with a sitting room and balcony, it's the perfect comfortable retreat. The backyard offers a refreshing pool, great for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, entertainment, and restaurants, this home provides accessibility without compromising comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this welcoming property your home sweet home
